// Single source of truth for the iOS build number (CFBundleVersion).
//
// This is bumped automatically during a Release archive by the "Bump Build
// Number" build phase on the GatherLists app target, and by `make bump`. The
// build phase also patches the freshly-built app/appex Info.plists, so the
// archive that triggers the bump already carries the new number (no off-by-one).
// It lives here (not in the .pbxproj) so it can be edited while Xcode is open
// without conflicts, and so bumping never mutates the project mid-build.
CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION = 64
